                    </p>
                    <p>
                        With a mother's broken heart I write this message to thank you from the bottom of my heart for every action you did to help Marcos Z"L this past 3 years and 4 months. I was blessed by being his mother, the best present God could have given me. He left a giant hole in this world. We can all learn a lot from him: he never complained about anything, was happy every second of his life, he always had the perfect joke, he always had a smile on his face, he always had a song to make you better, he never suffered or surrendered. He fought this head on and always said, I am ok, we are all going to be ok. We should all be thankful for every second we have in this world and think of him. We will never forget him, he was our pilar and he will always be. He will give us the strength to keep going forward.
